 ('153', '240', '4', '1', 'en_gb', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Reconfigure.io secures seed funding\",\"slug\":\"reconfigure-io-secures-seed-funding\",\"postDate\":1505907605,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"62\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"leadCopy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Manchester, UK, 26th Oct 2016\\u200a&mdash;\\u200aReconfigure.io, a computing accelerator specialist, completes a seed-funding round from a group of senior angel investors from the UK, Switzerland and the US.<\\/p>\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"bodyCopy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Reconfigure.io is a step forward in enterprise computing capabilities through a new approach in hardware acceleration for the mass engineering marketplace. The platform-as-a-service (PaaS) enables developers to run code on FPGA\\u2019s as easily as they deploy to servers. Reconfigure.io provides multiple benefits to the current generation of application programmers\\u200a&mdash;\\u200aranging from increasing computing performance by factors from 10\\u2013100x to decreas development cycles from days to minutes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Rob Taylor, the founder and CEO of Reconfigure.io says \\u201cOur platform is designed by individuals with tremendous experience in the hardest problems in the modern computational landscape. The early partnerships with industry leaders has already validated our approach\\u2019s value. This seed round provides us with the opportunity to further expand our team and to progress far towards productising our first GA, planned in early 2017\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Reconfigure.io is in early-stage partnerships with IBM, Xilinx, and Rackspace, three leaders in the cloud and hardware industries. The company is debuting its technology at IBM\\u2019s OpenPOWER Summit Europe in Barcelona, 26th-28th October 2016.<\\/p>\"}}},\"69\":\"\",\"70\":{\"metadata\":{\"enableMetaDetailsSearch\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsOpenGraph\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsTwitterCard\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsGeo\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsRobots\":\"0\",\"schemaTypeId\":\"\",\"schemaOverrideTypeId\":\"\",\"title\":\"\",\"description\":\"\",\"keywords\":\"\",\"ogType\":\"\",\"ogTitle\":\"\",\"ogDescription\":\"\",\"ogImage\":\"\",\"ogTransform\":\"\",\"ogAudio\":\"\",\"ogVideo\":\"\",\"twitterCard\":\"summary\",\"twitterTitle\":\"\",\"twitterDescription\":\"\",\"twitterImage\":\"\",\"twitterTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCreator\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"placename\":\"\",\"latitude\":\"\",\"longitude\":\"\",\"robots\":{\"noindex\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"noarchive\":\"\",\"noimageindex\":\"\",\"noodp\":\"\",\"noydir\":\"\"}}}}}', '2017-09-20 11:40:05', '2017-09-20 11:40:05', 'e8a66019-c246-42af-bb25-d0339f593dbc'),
 ('154', '244', '4', '1', 'en_gb', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"European Market Adopting OpenPOWER Technology\",\"slug\":\"european-market-adopting-openpower-technology\",\"postDate\":1505907691,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"62\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"leadCopy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Widespread Adoption of OpenPOWER Technology Across Europe for Artificial Intelligence, Deep Learning and World-Advancing Research including the Human Brain Project<\\/p><p>Developer Momentum Continues with European OpenPOWER Developer Cloud, CAPI SNAP Framework Tool, OpenPOWER READY Accelerator Boards and Winners of Developer Challenge Revealed<\\/p><p>European OpenPOWER Community Grows to 60 Members Strong<\\/p>\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"imageFile\":[\"243\"]}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"bodyCopy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><b>Barcelona, Spain, October 27, 2016:&nbsp;<\\/b>At the inaugural OpenPOWER European Summit, the OpenPOWER Foundation made a series of announcements today detailing the rapid growth, adoption and support of OpenPOWER across the continent. Members announced:<\\/p>\"}}},\"69\":\"\",\"70\":{\"metadata\":{\"enableMetaDetailsSearch\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsOpenGraph\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsTwitterCard\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsGeo\":\"0\",\"enableMetaDetailsRobots\":\"0\",\"schemaTypeId\":\"\",\"schemaOverrideTypeId\":\"\",\"title\":\"\",\"description\":\"\",\"keywords\":\"\",\"ogType\":\"\",\"ogTitle\":\"\",\"ogDescription\":\"\",\"ogImage\":\"\",\"ogTransform\":\"\",\"ogAudio\":\"\",\"ogVideo\":\"\",\"twitterCard\":\"summary\",\"twitterTitle\":\"\",\"twitterDescription\":\"\",\"twitterImage\":\"\",\"twitterTransform\":\"\",\"twitterCreator\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"placename\":\"\",\"latitude\":\"\",\"longitude\":\"\",\"robots\":{\"noindex\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"noarchive\":\"\",\"noimageindex\":\"\",\"noodp\":\"\",\"noydir